				\begin{document}$$\Delta {G}_{{H}^{*}}$$\end{document}ΔGH∗ of –0.11 eV than that of Ti3-xCNO2-C-PtC (–0.15 eV). In addition, N atoms may enhance the electronic structure of the MXene surface, thus improving the HER. Therefore, the abundant N atoms in MXene play a crucial role in enhancing HER catalytic activity.
